#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Aniccavagga "
msgstr "2. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 19. Sahetudukkhasutta → dutiyahetusuttaṃ (bj) | hetu 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Sahetudukkhasutta "
msgstr "19. Suffering With Its Cause "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.24, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.19:1.3"
msgid "Yopi hetu yopi paccayo rūpassa uppādāya, sopi dukkho. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to form is also suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.19:1.4"
msgid "Dukkhasambhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, rūpaṃ kuto sukhaṃ bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since form is produced by what is suffering, how could it be happiness? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.5"
msgid "Vedanā dukkhā … "
msgstr "Feeling is suffering … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.6"
msgid "saññā dukkhā … "
msgstr "Perception is suffering … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.7"
msgid "saṅkhārā dukkhā … "
msgstr "Choices are suffering … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ. "
msgstr "Consciousness is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.19:1.9"
msgid "Yopi hetu yopi paccayo viññāṇassa uppādāya, sopi dukkho. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to consciousness is also suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.19:1.10"
msgid "Dukkhasambhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, viññāṇaṃ kuto sukhaṃ bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since consciousness is produced by what is suffering, how could it be happiness? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.19:1.12"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.19:1.13"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

